God Scorn			KEY:God Scorn ~ DemodandSpawn			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.TieflingRaceTrait.DemodandSpawnRaceTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,God Scorn ~ DemodandSpawn],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Tiefling (Demodand-Spawn)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Tiefling Demodand-Spawn]		DESC:Your contempt for the gods and their sad little priests makes it easier to shake off the effects of their prayers. You gain a +1 trait bonus on saving throws against divine spells.																														SOURCEPAGE:p.20
