Unearth Secrets		KEY:Unearth Secrets ~ DevilSpawn		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.TieflingRaceTrait.DevilSpawnRaceTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Unearth Secrets ~ DevilSpawn],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Tiefling (Devil-Spawn)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Tiefling Devil-Spawn]		DESC:You have a gift for recognizing secret desires. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Sense Motive checks when trying to get a hunch that might reveal a target's hidden vice, dark impulse, or any other craving it would not want publicly revealed.																				SOURCEPAGE:p.21
