Shift the Blame		KEY:Shift the Blame ~ DivSpawn		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.TieflingRaceTrait.DivSpawnRaceTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Shift the Blame ~ DivSpawn],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Tiefling (Div-Spawn)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Tiefling Div-Spawn]			DESC:You have learned many tricks to keep yourself from facing the consequences of your misdeeds.  You gain a +1 trait bonus on Bluff and Diplomacy checks made to convince someone that another person is actually at fault for your actions.																					SOURCEPAGE:p.21
