Superior Clutch		KEY:Superior Clutch ~ OniSpawn		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.TieflingRaceTrait.OniSpawnRaceTrait		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Superior Clutch ~ OniSpawn],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Tiefling (Oni-Spawn)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Tiefling Oni-Spawn]			DESC:Your hands not only are bigger than normal, but also have a strong grip useful for wielding large weapons. You gain a +1 trait bonus on damage rolls when using weapons intended for creatures of a larger size.																									SOURCEPAGE:p.22
