Vile Kiss			KEY:Vile Kiss ~ QlippothSpawn			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.TieflingRaceTrait.QlippothSpawnRaceTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Vile Kiss ~ QlippothSpawn],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]	PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Tiefling (Qlippoth-Spawn)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Tiefling Qlippoth-Spawn]		DESC:You have learned how to exploit the natural disgust you provoke when in close proximity to others.  You gain a +2 trait bonus on combat maneuver checks to perform a dirty trick combat maneuver for the purpose of making your opponent sickened.																			SOURCEPAGE:p.23
